      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, I just looked at the warehouse cost projections for those numbers and they're huge. We're gonna be drowning in storage fees if we buy that much upfront. \n\nCan you refine these numbers? I need the stockout rate to stay at 0% for the KPI, but try to find a better balance so we aren't overstocking everything by such a massive margin. Is there a way to hit that 0% target without just stocking the entire quarter's demand at once?",
